I cut a stick over there and I made a digging stick

then I poked it with this one

ru.sa ni.ma kr.m.tro a.tha.nzo we kran.bri.mth
but the deer went out of the forest and only the dogs came back
I walked and I went down

I went down and went up again
to the high ground called mdfi
wa.tik n tt.f ka.tan f w.thn sa.z.thi.fa zwn.th.ma

another small creek lies there. it always used to go lead from sazthi this way

then I killed plenty of gastol fish

I called for the dog, but nothing

I was paddling across to the other side
I came here. I arrived at the house
